#. module: theme_notes
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_notes.s_text_image
msgid ""
"Their early days were spent playing small gigs at local clubs, where they "
"rapidly gained a reputation for their high-energy performances and "
"innovative sound. As they honed their craft, their fanbase grew, fueled by "
"word-of-mouth buzz and their undeniable chemistry on stage."
msgstr ""
"Hari-hari awal mereka dihabiskan memainkan peran kecil di klub-klub lokal, "
"dimana mereka membangun reputasi untuk petunjukkan bersemangat mereka dan "
"musik yang inovatif. Selagi mereka menajamkan ketrampilan mereka, fanbase "
"mereka berkembang, berkat berita dari mulut ke mulut dan chemistry mereka di "
"panggung."

#. module: theme_notes
#: model_terms:theme.ir.ui.view,arch:theme_notes.s_image_text
msgid ""
"Their music isn't just heard—it's felt, combining powerful melodies with "
"deeply relatable lyrics. Each song connects on a personal level, while their "
"unmatched musicianship drives every note forward."
msgstr ""
"Musik mereka tidak hanya terdengar—tapi dirasakan, menggabungkan melodi-"
"melodi kuat dengan lirik yang relatable. Setiap lagu akan dirasakan pada "
"level yang mendalam, di mana ketrampilan musik mereka mendorong setiap not "
"ke depan."

